item.title: CVE-2023-27889|2024-08-02T12:23:29.983Z -- liquid%20design%20ltd. -- liquid%20speech%20balloon
item.description: Cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in LIQUID SPEECH BALLOON versions prior to 1.2 allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to hijack the authentication of a user and to perform unintended operations by having a user view a malicious page.
